OL,6,FITV's will tackle the difficult
OL,7,Fsubject of suicide ideation in an
OL,8,Fongoing bullying storyline.
OL,10,FOver the past few months, viewers have
OL,11,Fseen teenager Liam Connor being
OL,12,Fbullied by a group of boys.
OL,14,FThe storyline has seen Liam being
OL,15,Fpressurised to vape and even having a
OL,16,Fknife pulled on him.
