OL,6,FHis mental health rapidly deteriorates
OL,7,Fand in an hour-long episode on
OL,8,FWednesday 14 February, viewers will
OL,9,Fdiscover the depths of Liam's despair
OL,10,Fas he is seen to search online ways to
OL,11,Fkill himself.
OL,13,FThe teenager will decide against
OL,14,Fending his own life, but in the
OL,15,Faftermath, Liam faces a long journey
OL,16,Fof recovery.
