OL,6,FSamia Longchambon who plays Maria
OL,7,FConnor, Liam's mum, said: "Maria is
OL,8,Freally paranoid, and understandably
OL,9,Fso, given that Liam is from the Connor
OL,10,Ffamily and we have all been through
OL,11,Fsimilar when Aidan Connor (Liam's
OL,12,Fcousin) committed suicide, so I don't
OL,13,Fthink she will be able to leave Liam
OL,14,Falone without fearing the worst.
