OL,6,F"This is going to be an ongoing issue
OL,7,Ffor Liam. We are considering all
OL,8,Foptions from homeschooling to
OL,9,Fcounselling. Of course when it comes
OL,10,Fto mental health, there's
OL,11,Funfortunately a massively long waiting
OL,12,Flist.
OL,14,F"I think the great thing about this
OL,15,Fstoryline is that we are doing it in
OL,16,Freal time. We aren't rushing this at
OL,17,Fall and doing everything as it would
OL,18,Fhappen."
