OL,6,FTo bring this story to the screen,
OL,7,FCoronation Street researchers and
OL,8,Fwriters have been working closely with
OL,9,Fthe National Bullying Helpline to
OL,10,Fensure Liam's story is told as
OL,11,Fauthentically and delicately as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,FIain Macleod, Executive Producer of
OL,15,FContinuing Drama at ITV, said: "This
OL,16,Fis a story that will have immense
OL,17,Fpersonal resonance for many people -
OL,18,Fit certainly did for some of the
OL,19,FCoronation Street team.
